*) Open the string by a turn of
the hand. (Turn the 3rd finger
and the hand to the right. It is
a certain swinging of the 3rd
finger, which amateurs are
fully acquainted with).

*) Strune przez odchylenie
reki uwolni¢é. (Obracanie 3.
palca w prawo. Jest to pewne-
gorodzaju kotysaniesie 3 palca,
ktérego szczegélnie dyletanci
uzywaja z upodobaniem).

*) Laisser libre la corde en
tournant la main. (Tourner le
3e doigt et la main droite.
C’est ce certain balancement
que les amateurs dominent 4
la perfection).

*) Liberare la corda girando la
mano. (Girare la mano assie-
me al terzo dito verso destra;
é quasi un’altalena del terzo
dito che i dilettanti sanno
usare bene).

