SCHOOL OF INTERPRETATION FOR
THE VIOLIN ON A MELODIC BASIS
IN 2 PARTS.

Ist PART.
INTRODUCTION TO SOLO PLAYING.

30 Violin solos and melodies with progressive material
developing the finger and bowing technic, the rhythm and p
formance from the first grade with a minimum knowledge
positions*) to the fourth grade.
Each solo is supplied from bar to bar with preparatory a
advanced finger- bow- and performance studies relating to 1
respective solo piece in order to improve greatly the technic
well as the beauty of formation of the tone.

